data.description: ONE Acre Opportunity with a 3-Bedroom 2-Bath Home located in Willis Texas, a fast-growing city, that has so much to offer! This property is perfect for someone who has a business and needs the space to park their trucks and trailers or for someone that wants to live on a property with more yard space than your average backyard. The home offers a spacious Living-room, a kitchen with plenty of cabinets and so much counter space for family gatherings, a formal dining room. No HOA, Low Property Tax Rates
